*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Include          ZBBUR0010_I01
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Module  USER_COMMAND_0100  INPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE user_command_0100 INPUT.
  DATA : ls_valid(1),
         ls_refresh(1) VALUE 'X'.

  "데이터 CRUD, 데이터 수정 및 삭제 가능
CALL METHOD G_GRID1->CHECK_CHANGED_DATA
 IMPORTING
   E_VALID = LS_VALID
 CHANGING
   C_REFRESH = LS_REFRESH.


  CASE ok_code.
    WHEN 'BACK'.
      LEAVE TO SCREEN 0.
    WHEN 'SAVE'.
      PERFORM SAVE.
    WHEN 'REGI'.
      PERFORM REGISTER.
    WHEN 'EDIT'.
      PERFORM EDIT.
    WHEN 'DELETE'.
      PERFORM DELETE.
  ENDCASE.
ENDMODULE.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      Module  EXIT  INPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*       text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE exit INPUT.
  CASE ok_code.
    WHEN 'EXIT' OR 'CANC'.
      LEAVE PROGRAM.
    WHEN OTHERS.
  ENDCASE.
ENDMODULE.

